                        в”Ӯв”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ - docker/login-action@v3                                в”Ӯв”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ - helm/kind-action@v1                                   в”Ӯв”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ - dorny/paths-filter@v3                                 в”Ӯв”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ - codecov/codecov-action@v4                             в”Ӯв”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ - actions/github-script@v7                              в”Ӯв”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳв”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n```\n\n### Component Relationships\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                      Workflow-to-Makefile Mapping                            в”Ӯ\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Workflow                  Makefile Target        Build Output               в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ  в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  main.yml                  docker-build          workloadmanager:latest      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  e2e.yml                   docker-build          workloadmanager:latest      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                            docker-build-router   agentcube-router:latest     в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                            docker-build-picod    picod:latest                в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                            e2e                   вҖ”                           в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                            e2e-clean             вҖ”                           в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  lint.yml                  lint                  вҖ”                           в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  test-coverage.yml         go test               coverage.out                в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  codegen-check.yml         gen-check             вҖ”                           в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  copyright-check.yml       gen-copyright         вҖ”                           в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  build-push-release.yml    docker-buildx-push    workloadmanager:${TAG}      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                            docker-buildx-push-   agentcube-router:${TAG}      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                              router                                             в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                            docker-buildx-push-   picod:${TAG}                 в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                              picod                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n```\n\n---\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### Workflow YAML Structure\n\nEach workflow follows this canonical structure:\n\n```yaml\nname: \"<Descriptive Workflow Name>\"\non:\n  <trigger-specification>\n\njobs:\n  <job-name>:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    if: <conditional-expression>\n    steps:\n      - name: \"<Step Description>\"\n        uses: <action-reference>\n        with:\n          <action-inputs>\n        env:\n          <environment-variables>\n```\n\n### Path Filter Definitions\n\n```yaml\nfilters:\n  lint:\n    - '**/*.go'\n    - 'go.mod'\n    - 'go.sum'\n    - '.golangci.yml'\n    - '.github/workflows/lint.yml'\n  \n  sdk:\n    - 'sdk-python/**'\n  \n  python:\n    - 'cmd/cli/**'\n    - 'sdk-python/**'\n    - 'example/**'\n    - 'test/**/*.py'\n    - 'pyproject.toml'\n    - '.github/workflows/python-lint.yml'\n  \n  coverage:\n    - '**'\n    - '!*.md'\n    - '!*.svg'\n    - '!*.png'\n  \n  codegen:\n    - 'pkg/apis/**'\n    - 'hack/**'\n    - '.github/workflows/**'\n    - 'Makefile'\n  \n  copyright:\n    - '**'\n    - '!*.md'\n    - '!*.svg'\n    - '!*.png'\n    - '!docs/**'\n    - '!.github/**'\n```\n\n### Workflow Output Variables\n\n```yaml\noutputs:\n  lint-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.lint }}\n  sdk-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.sdk }}\n  python-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.python }}\n  coverage-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.coverage }}\n  codegen-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.codegen }}\n  copyright-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.copyright }}\n```\n\n### Artifact Specifications\n\n```yaml\nartifacts:\n  go-coverage:\n    path: coverage.out\n    retention-days: 7\n    \n  e2e-logs:\n    path: e2e-logs/\n    retention-days: 7\n    if-no-files-found: warn\n```\n\n### Environment Variable Contract\n\n```yaml\nenv:\n  ARTIFACTS_PATH: ${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs\n  TAG: ${{ github.ref_type == 'tag' && github.ref_name || 'latest' }}\n  IMAGE_REGISTRY: ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}\n  WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE: workloadmanager:${{ env.TAG }}\n  ROUTER_IMAGE: agentcube-router:${{ env.TAG }}\n  PICOD_IMAGE: picod:${{ env.TAG }}\n  AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE: agentcube\n  WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL: http://localhost:${{ env.WORKLOAD_MANAGER_LOCAL_PORT }}\n  ROUTER_URL: http://localhost:${{ env.ROUTER_LOCAL_PORT }}\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### Workflow Trigger Specification\n\n```yaml\non:\n  pull_request:\n    branches:\n      - main\n      - 'release-*'\n    types:\n      - opened\n      - synchronize\n      - reopened\n  \n  push:\n    branches:\n      - main\n    tags:\n      - 'v*.*.*'\n      - 'v*.*.*-*'\n      - 'dify-plugin/v*'\n  \n  merge_group:\n  \n  workflow_call:\n    inputs:\n      CODECOV_TOKEN:\n        description: 'Codecov upload token'\n        required: false\n        type: string\n    secrets:\n      CODECOV_TOKEN:\n        description: 'Codecov token for coverage upload'\n        required: false\n  \n  pull_request_target:\n    branches:\n      - main\n      - 'release-**'\n    types:\n      - labeled\n      - synchronize\n```\n\n### GitHub Actions API Contract\n\n```yaml\nactions_api:\n  checkout:\n    uses: actions/checkout@v4\n    with:\n      fetch-depth: 0\n  \n  setup_go:\n    uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n    with:\n      go-version: '1.24'\n      cache: true\n  \n  setup_go_123:\n    uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n    with:\n      go-version: '1.23'\n      cache: true\n  \n  setup_go_1244:\n    uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n    with:\n      go-version: '1.24.4'\n      cache: true\n  \n  setup_python:\n    uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n    with:\n      python-version: '3.12'\n      cache: pip\n  \n  setup_python_310:\n    uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n    with:\n      python-version: '3.10'\n      cache: pip\n  \n  setup_buildx:\n    uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\n  \n  docker_login:\n    uses: docker/login-action@v3\n    with:\n      registry: ghcr.io\n      username: ${{ github.actor }}\n      password: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n  \n  paths_filter:\n    uses: dorny/paths-filter@v3\n    with:\n      filters: .github/workflows/filters.yaml\n  \n  kind_action:\n    uses: helm/kind-action@v1\n    with:\n      install_only: true\n      version: v0.30.0\n  \n  codecov:\n    uses: codecov/codecov-action@v4\n    with:\n      file: coverage.out\n      fail_ci_if_error: false\n      token: ${{ secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN }}\n  \n  github_script:\n    uses: actions/github-script@v7\n    with:\n      script: |\n        <inline-script>\n```\n\n### Makefile Target Contract\n\n```yaml\nmakefile_targets:\n  docker-build:\n    description: Build workload manager Docker image\n    prerequisites: Docker, Buildx\n    output: workloadmanager:latest\n    \n  docker-build-router:\n    description: Build router Docker image\n    prerequisites: Docker, Buildx\n    output: agentcube-router:latest\n    \n  docker-build-picod:\n    description: Build picod Docker image\n    prerequisites: Docker, Buildx\n    output: picod:latest\n    \n  docker-buildx-push:\n    description: Push workload manager to registry\n    env_vars:\n      - IMAGE_REGISTRY\n      - WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE\n    prerequisites: docker/login-action\n    \n  docker-buildx-push-router:\n    description: Push router to registry\n    env_vars:\n      - IMAGE_REGISTRY\n      - ROUTER_IMAGE\n    prerequisites: docker/login-action\n    \n  docker-buildx-push-picod:\n    description: Push picod to registry\n    env_vars:\n      - IMAGE_REGISTRY\n      - PICOD_IMAGE\n    prerequisites: docker/login-action\n    \n  lint:\n    description: Run golangci-lint\n    prerequisites: Go 1.24, .golangci.yml\n    \n  gen-check:\n    description: Verify generated code matches committed version\n    command_sequence:\n      - make gen-all\n      - git diff --exit-code\n    prerequisites: Go 1.24.4\n    \n  gen-copyright:\n    description: Generate copyright headers\n    prerequisites: moreutils (sponge)\n    \n  e2e:\n    description: Run E2E tests\n    prerequisites: Kind v0.30.0, Go 1.23, agent-sandbox CRDs\n    \n  e2e-clean:\n    description: Cleanup E2E resources\n    command: kind delete cluster --name agentcube-e2e\n```\n\n### Kind Cluster Configuration\n\n```yaml\nkind_cluster:\n  name: agentcube-e2e\n  version: v0.30.0\n  \n  images_loaded:\n    - registry.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/agent-sandbox-controller:v0.1.1\n    - python:3.9-slim\n    - workloadmanager:latest\n    - agentcube-router:latest\n    - picod:latest\n    - redis:7-alpine\n  \n  crds_applied:\n    - https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases/download/v0.1.1/manifest.yaml\n    - https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases/download/v0.1.1/extensions.yaml\n  \n  helm_chart:\n    path: manifests/charts/base\n    release: agentcube\n    namespace: agentcube\n    values:\n      redis.address: redis.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:6379\n      redis.password: \"\"\n      workloadmanager.image.repository: workloadmanager\n      workloadmanager.image.tag: latest\n      router.image.repository: agentcube-router\n      router.image.tag: latest\n      router.rbac.create: true\n      router.serviceAccountName: agentcube-router\n```\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Workflow Failure Categories\n\n| Category | Description | Recovery Action |\n|----------|-------------|-----------------|\n| `BuildFailure` | Docker build or compilation error | Log output, fail job |\n| `LintFailure` | golangci-lint or Ruff violations | Report violations, fail job |\n| `TestFailure` | Unit test or E2E test failure | Upload artifacts, fail job |\n| `CodegenDrift` | Generated code differs from committed | Show diff, fail job |\n| `CopyrightDrift` | Copyright headers mismatch | Show diff, fail job |\n| `SpellingError` | codespell detected typos | Report errors, fail job |\n| `RegistryAuthFailure` | Docker login failed | Log error, fail job |\n| `KindSetupFailure` | Kind cluster creation failed | Upload logs, fail job |\n| `CoverageUploadFailure` | Codecov upload failed | Continue (non-blocking) |\n\n### Conditional Failure Handling\n\n```yaml\nfailure_handling:\n  e2e_failure:\n    if: failure()\n    steps:\n      - name: Upload E2E logs\n        uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4\n        with:\n          name: e2e-logs\n          path: e2e-logs/\n  \n  e2e_cleanup:\n    if: always()\n    steps:\n      - name: Cleanup E2E\n        run: make e2e-clean\n        continue-on-error: true\n  \n  coverage_upload:\n    if: success()\n    steps:\n      - name: Upload to Codecov\n        uses: codecov/codecov-action@v4\n        with:\n          fail_ci_if_error: false\n```\n\n### Path Filter Skip Logic\n\n```yaml\npath_filter_skip:\n  pattern: |\n    if: steps.filter.outputs.<filter-name> != 'true'\n    run: echo \"No <filter-name> changes detected, skipping job\"\n    \n  skip_job: |\n    jobs:\n      <job-name>:\n        if: ${{ needs.<previous-job>.outputs.<filter-name> == 'true' }}\n```\n\n### Secrets Handling\n\n```yaml\nsecrets_contract:\n  GITHUB_TOKEN:\n    scope: write (for gh pr create)\n    usage: Registry login, GitHub API\n    built_in: true\n  \n  CODECOV_TOKEN:\n    scope: read\n    usage: Codecov upload authentication\n    optional: true\n    declared_in: workflow_call\n    \n  PLUGIN_ACTION:\n    scope: write (for cross-repo checkout and PR)\n    usage: Dify plugin publish workflow\n    required_for: dify-plugin-publish.yml\n```\n\n### Timeout Configuration\n\n```yaml\ntimeout_config:\n  job_timeout:\n    default: 30m\n    e2e: 45m\n    \n  step_timeout:\n    go_test: 10m\n    e2e_run: 30m\n    docker_build: 15m\n    docker_push: 20m\n```\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Workflow Validation Matrix\n\n| Workflow | Validation Method | Test Command |\n|----------|-------------------|--------------|\n| `main.yml` | Docker build success | `make docker-build` |\n| `e2e.yml` | E2E test execution | `make e2e` in Kind cluster |\n| `lint.yml` | golangci-lint pass | `make lint` |\n| `python-sdk-tests.yml` | pytest pass | `python -m pytest tests/ -v` |\n| `python-lint.yml` | Ruff pass | `ruff check . --config pyproject.toml` |\n| `test-coverage.yml` | Coverage generation | `go test -race -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/...` |\n| `codegen-check.yml` | No drift | `make gen-check && git diff --exit-code` |\n| `copyright-check.yml` | No drift | `make gen-copyright && git diff --exit-code` |\n| `codespell.yml` | No spelling errors | `codespell --check-filenames .` |\n| `build-push-release.yml` | Registry push | `make docker-buildx-push` (with registry auth) |\n| `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Plugin package | `dify-plugin package` |\n| `workflows-approve.yml` | API approval | GitHub API `approveWorkflowRun` |\n\n### E2E Test Sequence\n\n```yaml\ne2e_test_sequence:\n  setup:\n    - name: Create Kind cluster\n      command: kind create cluster --name agentcube-e2e\n    \n    - name: Load images\n      command: kind load docker-image <image-list>\n    \n    - name: Apply CRDs\n      command: kubectl apply --validate=false -f <crd-urls>\n    \n    - name: Install Helm chart\n      command: helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base\n    \n    - name: Port-forward services\n      command: kubectl port-forward svc/<service>\n    \n    - name: Health check\n      command: curl http://localhost:<port>/health\n    \n  test_execution:\n    - name: Go E2E tests\n      env:\n        WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL: http://localhost:8080\n        ROUTER_URL: http://localhost:8081\n        API_TOKEN: <generated-token>\n      command: go test -v ./test/e2e/...\n    \n    - name: Python E2E tests\n      command: python test_codeinterpreter.py\n    \n  cleanup:\n    - name: Delete Kind cluster\n      command: kind delete cluster --name agentcube-e2e\n      if: always()\n    \n    - name: Remove temp files\n      command: rm -rf /tmp/agent-sandbox\n      if: always()\n```\n\n### Coverage Test Specification\n\n```yaml\ncoverage_test_spec:\n  command: |\n    go test -race -v \\\n      -coverprofile=coverage.out \\\n      -coverpkg=./pkg/... \\\n      ./pkg/...\n  \n  package_scope: ./pkg/...\n  \n  race_detector: enabled\n  \n  output:\n    coverage.out: coverage profile\n    step_summary: coverage percentage\n  \n  upload:\n    provider: Codecov\n    file: coverage.out\n    fail_on_error: false\n```\n\n### Python Test Specification\n\n```yaml\npython_test_spec:\n  sdk_tests:\n    working_directory: sdk-python\n    python_version: '3.12'\n    setup:\n      - pip install pytest\n      - pip install -e .\n    command: python -m pytest tests/ -v\n  \n  e2e_python:\n    working_directory: test/e2e\n    python_version: '3.12'\n    venv: /tmp/agentcube-e2e-venv\n    setup:\n      - python3 -m venv $E2E_VENV_DIR\n      - pip install -e ./sdk-python\n    command: python test_codeinterpreter.py\n```\n\n### Workflow Self-Test Commands\n\n```yaml\nworkflow_self_test:\n  validate_yaml:\n    command: yamllint .github/workflows/*.yml\n    \n  check_syntax:\n    command: gh workflow view <workflow-name>\n    \n  test_trigger:\n    command: gh workflow run <workflow-name> --ref <branch>\n    \n  verify_artifacts:\n    command: gh run download <run-id>\n```\n\n---\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\n.github/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ workflows/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ main.yml                    # PR Docker build verification\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ e2e.yml                     # E2E tests on Kind\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ lint.yml                    # Go lint with path filter\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ python-sdk-tests.yml        # Python SDK pytest\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ python-lint.yml             # Python Ruff lint\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ test-coverage.yml           # Go coverage + Codecov\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ codegen-check.yml           # Generated code drift\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ copyright-check.yml         # Copyright header check\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ codespell.yml               # Spelling verification\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ build-push-release.yml      # Multi-arch image push\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ dify-plugin-publish.yml     # Dify plugin release\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ workflows-approve.yml       # Auto-approve trusted\nв””в”Җв”Җ filters.yaml                    # (optional) Centralized path filters\n```\n\n### Workflow File Size Estimates\n\n| Workflow | Estimated Lines | Complexity |\n|----------|-----------------|------------|\n| `main.yml` | ~30 | Low |\n| `e2e.yml` | ~80 | High |\n| `lint.yml` | ~50 | Medium |\n| `python-sdk-tests.yml` | ~40 | Low |\n| `python-lint.yml` | ~50 | Medium |\n| `test-coverage.yml` | ~60 | Medium |\n| `codegen-check.yml` | ~50 | Medium |\n| `copyright-check.yml` | ~50 | Medium |\n| `codespell.yml` | ~80 | Medium |\n| `build-push-release.yml` | ~100 | High |\n| `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | ~120 | High |\n| `workflows-approve.yml` | ~70 | High |\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### GitHub Actions Dependencies\n\n| Action | Version | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|---------|\n| `actions/checkout` | v4 | Repository checkout with history |\n| `actions/setup-go` | v5 | Go toolchain (versions 1.23, 1.24, 1.24.4) |\n| `actions/setup-python` | v5 | Python toolchain (versions 3.10, 3.12) |\n| `docker/setup-buildx-action` | v3 | Docker Buildx setup |\n| `docker/login-action` | v3 | Container registry authentication |\n| `helm/kind-action` | v1 | Kind cluster tooling (v0.30.0) |\n| `dorny/paths-filter` | v3 | Path-based job filtering |\n| `codecov/codecov-action` | v4 | Coverage report upload |\n| `actions/upload-artifact` | v4 | Artifact storage |\n| `actions/github-script` | v7 | GitHub API scripting |\n\n### Tool Dependencies\n\n| Tool | Version | Purpose |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| Go | 1.23, 1.24, 1.24.4 | Go builds and tests |\n| Python | 3.10, 3.12 | Python lint and SDK tests |\n| Docker | latest | Container builds |\n| Buildx | latest | Multi-architecture builds |\n| Kind | v0.30.0 | Kubernetes in Docker |\n| golangci-lint | (project default) | Go linting |\n| Ruff | latest | Python linting |\n| pytest | latest | Python testing |\n| codespell | latest | Spelling check |\n| yq | latest | YAML processing (dify-plugin) |\n| dify-plugin CLI | 0.0.6 | Plugin packaging |\n\n### External Resources\n\n| Resource | URL | Purpose |\n|----------|-----|---------|\n| agent-sandbox CRDs | github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases | Kind cluster setup |\n| agent-sandbox controller | registry.k8s.io/agent-sandbox | E2E dependencies |\n| python:3.9-slim | Docker Hub | Echo agent workload |\n| redis:7-alpine | Docker Hub | Session store |\n| ghcr.io | GitHub Container Registry | Image publication |\n| Codecov | codecov.com | Coverage reporting |\n| dify-plugins repo | github.com/langgenius/dify-plugins | Plugin publication |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Workflow Naming Convention\n\n- Filenames: lowercase with hyphens (e.g., `main.yml`, `e2e.yml`)\n- Workflow `name`: descriptive titles (e.g., \"Agentcube CI Workflow\")\n- Job names: descriptive with underscores (e.g., `build`, `e2e-test`, `coverage`)\n- Step names: action-oriented descriptions\n\n### Path Filter Pattern\n\n- Use `dorny/paths-filter@v3` for all path-sensitive workflows\n- Filters defined inline or in separate `filters.yaml` file\n- Output used in `if:` conditions for job skipping\n- Inverted patterns (`!*.md`) for exclusion\n\n### Kind Cluster Isolation\n\n- Use `install_only: true` to prevent `helm/kind-action` from creating cluster\n- Cluster name: `agentcube-e2e`\n- Cleanup in `always()` block to ensure resource release\n- Logs collected in `ARTIFACTS_PATH` on failure\n\n### Registry Authentication\n\n- Use `GITHUB_TOKEN` (built-in) for `ghcr.io` authentication\n- No long-lived secrets required for main workflow\n- `PLUGIN_ACTION` secret for cross-repo operations in dify-plugin workflow\n\n### Coverage Upload Strategy\n\n- Upload `coverage.out` as artifact first\n- Codecov upload is non-blocking (`fail_ci_if_error: false`)\n- `CODECOV_TOKEN` optional via `workflow_call` secrets\n\n### First-time Contributor Handling\n\n- Use `pull_request_target` for access to repo secrets\n- Check contributor PR count via GitHub API\n- Approve `action_required` workflow runs for trusted contributors\n- `ok-to-test` label overrides first-time check\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Spec: `changes/AR-034/spec.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-034/delta-spec.md`\n- Proposal: `changes/AR-034/proposal.md`\n- Tasks: `changes/AR-034/tasks.md`\n- CI/CD Reference: `ci-cd/design.md`\n- CI/CD Specification: `ci-cd/spec.md`\n- E2E Test Script: `test/e2e/run_e2e.sh`\n- Makefile: `Makefile`\n- GitHub Actions Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/actions\n- Kind Docs: https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/\n- Docker Buildx: https://docs.docker.com/buildx/working-with-buildx/"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-034/design.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-034/design.md","time":{"start":1775889307360,"end":1775889307395}}}}
